ict Cumberbatch Joins 'Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, Spy' |date=2010-08-16 |accessdate=2010-09-04 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919210657/http://www.cinematical.com/2010/08/16/benedict-cumberbatch-joins-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。这部电影改编自[[约翰·勒卡雷|约翰·勒卡雷]]的同名小说，收获了很高的评价<ref name=RTTTSS>{{cite web|title=Tinker Tailor Soldier, Spy 2011|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tinker_tailor_soldier_spy/|work=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Flixster, Inc.|accessdate=2013-02-03|archive-date=2012-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308212851/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tinker_tailor_soldier_spy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

